CS_PAINTBALL_SOURCE_FINAL

Remake of CS_PAINTBALL from CS 1.6


Fixes and changes on this map respecting to my other CS Paintball Version.

1. New textures
2. Improved lightning
3. Added more props and cover
4. Ladder Textures fixed
5. Fixed a crate outside the map :P
6. Green crates textures got fixed and look more CS1.6sh



Map for 32 Players. 16 on each team.
Includes nav. files if you wish to play with bots.

Map weight: 2.5Mbs
